 a \land \neg b \in I ~~\text{ and }~~ b \land \neg a \in I \tag{1}
 a \lor (b \land \neg a) = (a \lor b) \land (a \lor \neg a) = a \lor b = (b \lor a) \land (b \lor \neg b) = b \lor (a \land \neg b) \tag{2}
